file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /pet/{petId}/uploadImage:
    get:
      summary: uploads an image
      description: ""
      operationId: getSomething
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          description: ID of pet to update
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: additionalMetadata
          in: query
          description: Additional Metadata
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: successful operation
